er-box; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; width: 360px; height: 250px;\" name=\"aswift_0\" width=\"360\" height=\"250\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins></div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-4 text-center col-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 370px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important; text-align: center !important;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">This was fixed after lots of controversies ever since the \'witchcraft conference\' was made public. Meanwhile, Christian Association of Nigeria (CAN), had earlier kicked against the conference saying it has evil motives. However, the organisers have explained that the conference is solely for academic purposes.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none;\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,', '1574696066_thump.jpeg', '2019-11-25 15:34:26');
