(39, 'Offa Poly Graduates Killed on Their Way to NYSC Orientation Camp', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">Yesterday, November 28, students of the Federal Polytechnic Offa, Kwara State, were involved in a fatal accident along Kano road which took the lives of some students. The student were reportedly going for their NYSC 3 weeks Orientation Camp Exercise when tragic struck.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">Some of the students took to Facebook to mourn those that has been reported dead.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none;\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" /></p>', '1575032598_thump.jpeg', '2019-11-29 13:03:18');
