(40, '200l Student Arrested for Participating in NYSC', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">The National Youth Service Corps (NYSC) arrested a certain 200-level student for allegedly obtaining a fake degree certificate and partaking in the ongoing orientation exercise in Zamfara state camp. It was said that the NYSC last Friday arrested the student who was only identified as Rose, a 200-level Journalism undergraduate in a university in Cotonou, Benin republic. This arrest has been confirmed by the NYSC Director- General, Brig. Gen. Shuaibu Ibrahim.</p>\r\n<div class=\"row t_container\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">\r\n<div class=\"mb-4 text-center col-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 370px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important; text-align: center !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; background-color: transparent;\">The DG said the Benin Republic university wrote to inform the scheme after seeing photographs of \"Rose\" in the NYSC uniform while in camp. These photographs were seen on her social media page. She was participating in the Batch C stream 1 orientation course before she was apprehended. He also noted that the student was brought to the FCT, Abuja, also to the office of the Department of State Services for further investigations.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-4 text-center col-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 370px; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; flex: 0 0 100%; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important; text-align: center !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">The DG has warned that the NYSC would fish out fake graduates and certificates, and also that anyone arrested would be duly prosecuted.The DG is quoted to have said, &ldquo;The clampdown on fake graduates and certificates is yielding more results. On Friday, one of the universities in Cotonou, Benin Republic saw their 200-level student in the NYSC uniform on the social media. She is supposed to be a 200-level of the university studying journalism.\" &ldquo;But she went and purchased a fake certificate from another Benin Republic university and now served in the camp in Zamfara. So, her classmates saw her on the social media and raised the alarm to the university, which then alerted and wrote me.\"</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">&ldquo;The university said they recognised the efforts of the scheme in nabbing fake graduates and they were not a party to her fake certificate. So we got her arrested in Zamfara. She was brought to Abuja and we have arranged with the DSS to take her away.&rdquo;</p>', '1575037542_thump.jpeg', '2019-11-29 14:25:42'),
(41, 'Breaking : Ifeanyi Ubah Football Club Attacked In Lokoja By Armed Gang Wearing NYSC Uniform Near Lokoja', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Players of FC Ifeanyi Ubah (Anambra Warriors) who were traveling to Kano for their scheduled NPFL matchday 6 fixture against Jigawa Golden Stars ran into a group of armed robbers dressed in NYSC uniforms, operating at Kabba junction, near Lokoja in Kogi state.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To the glory of God, no life was lost. However, the driver was shot while some members of the coaching crew and players were critically injured. The affected persons are currently being treated and are responding to treatment.</p>\r\n<p>We wish to use this medium to appeal to the Federal Government as well as football regulatory bodies; Nigerian Football Federation(NFF) and the League Management Company (LMC) to further intensify security efforts to ensure the safety of teams who often have no choice than to travel long distances by road, especially clubs owned by Private investors who are made to invest their hard earned money in the growth and development of Nigerian football.</p>\r\n<p>Conclusively, fans, well wishers, supporters and Nigerians in general are kindly urged to keep the entire management, coaching staff and players of FC Ifeanyi Ubah in their prayers in this moment of despair.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1575059917_thump.jpg', '2019-11-29 20:38:37'),
(42, 'Auto crashes kill 143 in Edo', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">The Edo Sector Command of the Federal Road Safety Corps (FRSC) has said that 143 persons were killed in road safety crashes in the state due to absent-mindedness of drivers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">Mr Anthony Oko, State sector commander of the corps revealed this to NAN on Thursday in Benin, at the flag-off of the 2019 Ember month campaign by the corps.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">Oko said that the figure which represents 37 per cent of accidents in the state, was between January and October.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">He said the deaths were recorded from 170 road traffic cases, which involved 351 vehicles, while 664 persons were recorded injured.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">He also revealed that 136 people were killed in 2018 due to the same factor, adding that the figure represented 39 per cent.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">Oko explained that out of 290 probable causes of crashes that year, 113 were deduced to be by drivers&rsquo; absent-mindedness.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">He added that the figure was from 206 total crashes that happened within that period, with 387 vehicles involved and 801 persons injured.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">The sector commander said that the theme for the 2019 ember months campaign is &ldquo;Road Crash is Absence of Mind: Stay Alert, Stay Alive&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">He noted that absent-mindedness was a topical issue that requires the attention of the state and relevant stakeholders as the yuletide approaches to increase awareness.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">He explained that some of the road traffic crashes that emanated from drivers absent-mindedness were from the use of phone while driving, fatigue, driving under the influence and dangerous driving.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">Other causes include wrongful overtaking and loss of control of vehicles</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'PT Serif\', sans-serif; line-height: 24.8px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; widows: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\">Oko stressed the need for all to adhere strictly to road traffic laws and regulations at all levels and collaborate with the command to enforce traffic laws, ensure prompt rescue services as well as educate all categories of road users.</p>', '1575097112_thump.jpg', '2019-11-30 06:58:32'),
(46, 'WAEC Withdraws Certificate of 1992 and 1993 Candidates due to Malpractice', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">&nbsp;list of candidates whose certificates have been withdrawn by the West African Examinations Council (WAEC), for examination malpractice between December 1992 and 1993 have been released by the commission. The list of affected WAEC candidates was published in the weekly bulletin of the Joint Admissions and Matriculation Board, JAMB, released on Monday. The nature of the malpractices of the affected candidates was found to be on impersonation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">He</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">nce, JAMB has noted that, it would be partnering with the National Identity Management Commission (NIMC), to curb the menace of impersonation by, enforcing its candidates&rsquo; registration for the national identity number.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1575550288_thump.jpeg', '2019-12-05 12:51:28'),
(47, 'BREAKING NEWS: N7.1bn fraud: Orji Kalu bags 12 years imprisonment.', '<p>BREAKING NEWS: N7.1bn fraud: Orji Kalu bags 12 years imprisonment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>IMAGE: Orji Kalu (arrowed) being led away into holding cell. Photo: Ramon Oladimeji</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&hellip;Court winds up company</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Federal High Court in Lagos has convicted a former governor of Abia State, Orji Uzor Kalu, who was charged with N7.1bn fraud.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The court found him and his co-defendants guilty of the entire 39 counts filed against them by the Economic and Financial Crimes Commission.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Justice Mohammed Idris sentenced Kalu to 12 years&rsquo; imprisonment while he ordered the winding up of Kalu&rsquo;s company, Slok Nigeria Limited, charged as third defendant in the case.</p>', '1575574031_thump.jpg', '2019-12-05 19:27:11'),
(48, 'Evangelist Reinhard Bonnke has died today being 7th Dec, 2019.', '<p>#Breaking sad News!</p>\r\n<p>Evangelist Reinhard Bonnke has died today being 7th Dec, 2019. May his soul RIPðŸ˜­ðŸ˜­</p>\r\n<p>Born April 19, 1940.... From Germany</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>More news coming.....</p>', '1575739768_thump.jpg', '2019-12-07 17:29:28'),
(50, 'I just want justiceâ€- Mother of River State Final Year Student Matilda Cries Out', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">Mother of Matilda Itonyo, a final year student of River State University who was stabbed to death in her room is crying out for justice. Matilda was stabbed to death and allegedly raped on the 10th of December by unidentified persons, if you missed it.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">The mother of the deceased has been in pains and seeking for the attention of the government to help her fight for justice as her daughter was her hope and future.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mt-4 mb-4 text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fcfcfc; margin-top: 1.5rem !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important; text-align: center !important;\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://myschool.ng/storage/blog/zuAzVm4D55j05hU7GsrZufGsdtyEI9L3iV354LJs.jpeg\" alt=\"&ldquo;I just want justice&rdquo;- Mother of River State Final Year Student Matilda Cries Out\" /></div>\r\n<blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">&ldquo;I just want justice. Just look at me. The girl has struggled&hellip; struggled to final year for Law. My Hope&hellip;My Future. Part of my flesh and blood is going out of me. My tomorrow&rsquo;s Glory is going down i need justice l can&rsquo;t bear it. Matilda is somebody everybody wants to to be a mother to. Matilda is somebody everybody is saying how I wish l have Baby like this one. How can they cut down the life of my daughter like this? I need Government to help me. I need justice.&rdquo; she said weeping</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">&ldquo;My daughter struggled to make it and somebody will just come to take her life like that. Its a very painful thing. l don&rsquo;t even know what to do. Let the Government come to my aid.&nbsp; People of Nigeria&hellip; People of Bayelsa people of Rivers State please come to my aid to get the killers of my daughter.&rdquo; my daughter like this? I need Government to help me. I need justice.&rdquo; she said weeping</p>\r\n</blockquote>', '1576334362_thump.jpeg', '2019-12-14 14:39:22'),
(51, 'Angry youths set church in Ondo ablaze following rumors a missing baby was found buried at the altar', '<p>Angry youths in Akure, the Ondo state capital, have set ablaze the Sotitobire Miracle Church after the corpse of a one-year-old boy declared missing in the church in November, was allegedly exhumed from the church altar.</p>\r\n<p>Recall that sometime in November, baby Gold Kolawole was declared missing in the church. He had gone to the church with his mother who dropped him off at the children\'s department in the church but when she returned to pick him up after the close of church, he was nowhere to be found. The church workers were also unable to give her an explanation as to his whereabouts.</p>\r\n<p>Alfa Babatunde, the founder of the church was arrested following the incident, and has been in the custody of the DSS.</p>\r\n<p>This morning, the youths acting on rumors that the corpse of the child was allegedly exhumed from the altar, besieged the church and set it on fire.</p>', '1576698469_thump.png', '2019-12-18 19:47:50'),
(52, 'DONALD TRUMP REMAINS IN OFFICE AS USA PRESIDENT...DESPITE HOUSE DEMOCRATS IMPEACHMENT', '<p>Donald Trump has Mocked Democrats for Impeaching him. He established his Confidence in the Senate by believing that the \"Senate will do the right thing\" When brought the politically motivated Charges against him.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is an established fact that a historic trial in the Senate is expected to begin early next year, giving senators the final say on whether to acquit the 45th president or convict and remove him from office. Until the Senate dismisses Trump, He still remains in Office. Meanwhile the acquittal and retainment of Donald Trump in&nbsp; power as President of the United States by the Republican-controlled chamber is very likely possible.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is true that US President Donald Trump was impeached for abuse of power in a historic vote in the House of Representatives on Wednesday. This result has now set up a trial in the Senate on removing him from office and until the Senate rules, Trump remains in Office.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With an eventual&nbsp; vote of 229 to 198&nbsp; in the Democratic-controlled House, the 45th US president could become the third occupant of the White House in American history to be dismissed if the Senate fails to upturn the house verdict.</p>', '1576794267_thump.jpg', '2019-12-19 22:24:27'),
(53, 'Man Shares Photos of How He Started the Decade and Ends It Receiving an Award from Queen Elizabeth', '<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">A Tanzanian man has shared the photographic moments of transition in his life on social media. The man who started the decade struggling with his laptop from his room, ended the decade receiving an ward from Queen Elizabeth. Given Edward took to Twitter to share photos of how his decade started and how it ended. Though his beginning was humble, he ended this decade by receiving an award from Her Majesty the Queen for innovation and impact.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">He is the founder/CEO of Mtabe, a Tanzanian based tech company using artificial intelligence and SMS technology to deliver learning content to students in Tanzania who cannot afford textbooks and have no Internet access. It is so simple that an average African student needs no new device to get started</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">Given is also the founder of a similar App MyElimu, an Edtech discussion forum that allows peer learning and also allows Tanzanian Secondary School Students to discuss school activities.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '1577714611_thump.jpeg', '2019-12-30 14:03:31'),
(54, 'Iran Hoists The Red Flag Which Is A Traditional Symbol For War', '<p>Iran has declared war in a very old and traditional way against the United States Of America.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>According to report, this is the first time in centuries that they have hoisted a red flag.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>They have also pinpointed 35 &ldquo;key US targets&rdquo; for revenge after its top general was assassinated &ndash; with America expecting retaliation &ldquo;within weeks&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Hours later, rockets were fired near the US Embassy in Baghdad and at an airbase housing Ameri</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The chilling flag display is seen as a clear warning the Islamic Republic is ready to fulfil its worrying pledge to strike back at America and Donald Trump.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Chillingly written across the &ldquo;war flag&rdquo; were the words: &ldquo;Those who want to avenge the blood of Hussein&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Red flags in Shiite tradition symbolise both blood spilled unjustly and serve as a call to avenge a person who is slain.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It was hoisted above the important Jamkaran Mosque which is on the outskirts of the holy city of Qom, about 100 miles south of Tehran.</p>', '1578226372_thump.jpg', '2020-01-05 12:12:52'),
(55, 'Breaking News: Serving NYSC Member From Kogi State Commit Suicide ', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Miss Bolufemi Princess Motunrayo from Ijumu Local Government Area of Kogi State and a graduate of Banking and Finance, Prince Abubakar Audu University formally called Kogi State University currently a Batch C Youth Corps Member serving in&nbsp; Girls Secondary School, Ibagwa-Aka, Igbo-Eze South LGA, yesterday 10th of January, 2020 committed suicide with two bottles of snippers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In a short note she pen down before committing suicide, she said \"I did this because I see nothing worth living for in this world\".</p>', '1578769018_thump.jpg', '2020-01-11 18:56:58'),
(56, 'Bill Gates says if you want to be successful for a long time you have to be humble, his 10 advice to young people who want to be rich', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">He became a billionaire In 1987 at the age of 31 and the richest man in the world at the age of 39.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">Bill Gates has since then remain one of the richest people in the world. Kind of him, he has given various advice to young people over the years on how they can become rich and successful in life.</p>\r\n<div id=\"quads-ad4\" class=\"quads-location quads-ad4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">In this article, we want to share with you 10 of the most inspiring advice Bill Gates has given and we hope some of his advice change your life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">1.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Don&rsquo;t compare yourself with anyone in this world if you do so you are insulting yourself;</strong>&nbsp;Abraham Lincoln once wrote to the teacher of his child to make a request it was a simple one teaching that nobody in the world is bigger than him and he&rsquo;s bigger than no one. unfortunately, most young people in our world today, live their lives comparing themselves to every other person and end up trying to be everyone that&rsquo;s the part to unhappiness and failure in life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">Listen you are a unique being who is not designed to be good in everything but in something unique. Your Life&rsquo;s mission isn&rsquo;t to beat all the people in the game, your Life&rsquo;s mission is to know your own game. Be yourself, know that nobody is better than you and you are better than no one. You are simply a unique being who is capable of achieving something, no one else can achieve.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">2.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">To win big you sometimes have to take big risk;&nbsp;</strong>The best time of your life to be alive is when you are young because you have nothing to lose really nothing. Don&rsquo;t take life easy, don&rsquo;t live like everyone, don&rsquo;t just talk about your dreams, wake up and pursue it, don&rsquo;t make excuses, start with whatever you have wherever you are, get out and get lost.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">3.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Your exposure from a young age to the realities of the world is a super big things</strong>; Most people don&rsquo;t know what life really is until they are 40. Most people live with the illusion that life is all should be easy. Most people expect the government or their parents to solve their problems.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">The earlier you understand the realities of life the most successful will become. What then is the reality, well the reality is that life is tough and nobody will help you to solve your problems. We are sorry your parents or government cannot help you. The earlier you take 100% responsibility of your life the more successful become.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">4.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">You need a coach;</strong>&nbsp;it doesn&rsquo;t matter whether you&rsquo;re a basketball player or tennis player, a gymnast or a bridge player.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">In life, you will become the person you admire, if you don&rsquo;t have my anyone significant you will become nobody significant. You need a coach someone to inspire and challenge you, so once you believe in yourself your coach doesn&rsquo;t always have to be someone you have physical access to, you can decide to read books written by people who have achieved what you want to achieve, you can follow such people online and watched inspiring videos.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">Why is this important simple because, life is tough and most people around you don&rsquo;t know anything about success. If your father isn&rsquo;t successful, he can teach you how to be successful, if your siblings are mediocre, they can&rsquo;t inspire you to be successful. That&rsquo;s why you need to look outside your domain for someone who can inspire and challenge you.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">If you show people the problems and you show people the Solutions they will be moved to act;</strong>&nbsp;To be successful in life you must be able to lead people and to get them motivated towards a common goal. To motivate people into actions, you have to show them what the problem is and what can be done to create a solution. As a leader don&rsquo;t just give instructions, Let people know the reason why what has to be done needs to be done.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">6.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Success Is a lousy teacher it can seduce you into thinking you can&rsquo;t lose;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">if you want to be successful for a long time you have to be humble. So many people have been successful for few minutes because they got to a point where they started thinking that they know it all. People who was successful for a long time never stop learning because they know that they can lose if they don&rsquo;t keep on learning.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">7.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">I spend a lot of time reading;</strong>&nbsp;even as one of the richest man in the world for over three decades Bill Gates still remains of voracious reader because he understand that life changes every day and the only way to remain relevant is to keep on learning.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">In this day of social media, and interesting movies, how many young people take time to read good books anymore yet the books you read determine the future you will have just as Charlie Jones said you will be the same person in five years as you are today, except for the people you meet and the books you read.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">8.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">We start Life with many big dreams,</strong>Things we want to accomplish, create, build and experience but if you ask any one pass the age of 40 what happened to all the dreams they had they will most likely answer life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">According to a study, out of 60 people who are planning to start their own business right now, only one of them will ever start anything. Not only business people generally hate the Pains of taking action so much that even when they try to take action, the first failure or second, send them back to their comfort zone.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">Most people are dreamers because dream is sweet. You can&rsquo;t be healthy for long if you only eat sweet things. Dreams are sweet and everyone eats it. Action is bitter and that&rsquo;s why only few people take proactive, determined and persistent actions. Be Among The Few who get up from their dreams. Get out and get crazy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">9.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Our success has really been based on partnerships from the very beginning;</strong>The first Big success of Microsoft happened in the year 1980 when Bill Gates partnered with that the I.P.M. and ever since then Bill Gates has always been on the lookout to whom he can partner with, his passion for partnership was so strong that Microsoft even went to the extent of partnering with one of their biggest competitors Apple computer. What can you learn from this, two are better than one, you grow and succeed faster in life if you learn how to work with other people.</p>\r\n<div id=\"quads-ad3\" class=\"quads-location quads-ad3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #222222; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, \'.SFNSText-Regular\', \'San Francisco\', Roboto, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; color: #222222; background-color: #ffffff;\">10. Your most unhappy customers are your greatest source of learning explains itself you&rsquo;re unhappy clients and customers if you speak facts about what needs to be corrected in your products or services in summary if you want to be rich and successful in life don&rsquo;t compare yourself with anyone I never allow your dreams to die be strong and take risk and harmful read books and learn how to work and partner with other people.</p>', '1579592616_thump.jpg', '2020-01-21 07:43:37'),
(57, 'Court Remands Corps Member in Custody for the Murder of a 8-Year Old Boy in Kano State', '<div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fcfcfc; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">A corps member serving in Bebeji Local Government Area of Kano state identified as Jepthan Peter Makwin has been remanded by a magistrates&rsquo; court, sitting at Nomansland, on Friday December 3rd for the murder of a eight- year- old boy Hassan Sulaiman. The deceased was a class three pupil of Old Mosque Islamiyah School, Bebeji, his parents alledge that, Hassan Sulaiman, died after allegedly being beaten by Makwin in October 2019.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"mb-4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fcfcfc; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; background-color: transparent;\">Sulaiman Aliyu the victims&rsquo; father said, late Hassan and friends used to visit the NYSC Lodge to collect fruits, the Corps members were known to love children and freely gave them fruits. On the day of the incident, Hassan had gone back for more fruits after previously collecting some. He alledged that Makwin got angry on sighting Hassan trying to get more fruits and beat the boy, banging his head to the wall and kicked him severally which led to his death.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"text-justify\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #fcfcfc; text-align: justify !important;\">\r\n<div class=\"mt-4 mb-4 text-center\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 1.5rem !important; margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important; text-align: center !important;\"><img class=\"img-fluid\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://myschool.ng/storage/blog/IcH7uepepo5caxG9qDKERHandjOyZSVTSuiAixYM.jpeg\" alt=\"Court Remands Corps Member in Custody for the  Murder of a 8-Year Old Boy in Kano State\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Reacting to the report, the Kano state NYSC coordinator, Ladan Baba denied that Mr Makwin was responsible for Hassan&rsquo;s death. He said Makwin ran after little Hassan when he saw him trying to pluck fruits from the umbrella tree, In the process, the boy fell and hit his head on the wall of the entrance of the Lodge.</p>\r\n</div>', '1580114605_thump.jpeg', '2020-01-27 08:43:25'),
(58, 'Schoolgirl hit by Stray Bullet as Okada Riders and Police Clash in Lagos', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">A schoolgirl have become the recent victim of the clash between okada riders and police officers in Iyana Ipaja, Lagos since the state government banned their activities in the state. The clash has led to female student being hit by a stray bullet.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">In a video shared online, the schoolgirl can be seen lying motionless on the floor, Blood soaked through her school uniform and concerned people around her trying to stem the blood flow.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; background-color: #fcfcfc;\">The girl was eventually taken to the hospital where an operation was performed and the bullet was removed. She is currently recuperating in the hospital.</p>', '1581069335_thump.png', '2020-02-07 09:55:35'),
(59, 'â€œCORONAVIRUSâ€ .... Are we safe?', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is no more strange that the new coronavirus is a deadly virus originating from China.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Coronaviruses (CoV) are a large family of viruses that cause illness ranging from the common cold to more severe diseases such as Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS-CoV) and Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS-CoV). A novel coronavirus (nCoV) is a new strain that has not been previously identified in humans.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Coronaviruses are zoonotic, meaning they are transmitted between animals and people.&nbsp; Detailed investigations found that SARS-CoV was transmitted from civet cats to humans and MERS-CoV from dromedary camels to humans. Several known coronaviruses are circulating in animals that have not yet infected humans.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Common signs of infection include respiratory symptoms, fever, cough, shortness of breath and breathing difficulties. In more severe cases, infection can cause pneumonia, severe acute respiratory syndrome, kidney failure and even death.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Standard recommendations to prevent infection spread include regular hand washing, covering mouth and nose when coughing and sneezing, thoroughly cooking meat and eggs. Avoid close contact with anyone showing symptoms of respiratory illness such as coughing and sneezing.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Far enough Africa is still free from this disease but with the rapid spread of zoonotic infections, one could help but wonder if this particular virus is not already in Africa, however global statistics hasn&rsquo;t revealed any.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>#Getinformed</p>\r\n<p>#Bevigilant</p>\r\n<p>#Coronavirus</p>\r\n<p>#Dcuf</p>', '1581078051_thump.jpg', '2020-02-07 12:20:52'),
(60, 'Osun Secondary School Students Reveal Why They Raped Female NYSC Member After Arrest', '<p>Days after two students of Ogbogbo Baptist Grammar School were arrested by men of the special anti-robbery squad over alleged rape and robbery of a youth corper, the students identified as Bamidele Ayeni and Isiaka Akanji have revealed why they engaged in such act.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Reporter learnt that the incident reportedly occurred on the 13th Of February 2020 at about 7:30pm when the victim was returning from a church service at Ijari.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It was further learnt that Bamidele and Isiaka were said to have written series of letters to the youth corper, threatening she will be dealt with someday.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Revealing why the young corper was raped, the suspects confessed that the youth corper likes spending so much time in class, she doesn&rsquo;t allow us go on break time and she is fond of reporting us to the principal whenever she feels like.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The suspects stopped attending classes after they committed the crime and they were arrested at different locations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>According to local reports, the students were also members of a secret cult which they later admitted, saying they were both initiated 4 months ago by a person name igimu</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>School Proprietor rapes Corper on first day at Place Of Primary&hellip;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>He further said, they were promised higher position if they could kill at least 2 people.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Reacting on the incident, the officer in charge, CP Yomi Adamson said that the suspects will be charged to court after thorough investigation</p>', '1582008724_thump.jpg', '2020-02-18 06:52:05');
