(17, 'Okpalaugo', 'Okpalaugo.chukwuka1@gmail.com', 'Arsenal Set To Sack Unai Emery This Week And He Will Be Replaced By Arsenal\\\'s Ex-player', '<p>the Patience Of The Arsenal Fan Base Was Tested On Saturday As The Gunners Struggled To Pick A Point Against Relegation Threatened Side Southampton.</p>\r\n<p>the Fan Base Was Got Pissed To The Extent Of Booing All Their Players And Venting Their Frustrations On Aftv After The Game And They Voiced Their Frustration Towards Manager Unai Emery. There Has Been A Lot Of Negativity About Unai Emery, His Tactics And Player Management Since Last Season And Arsenal Are On The Verge Of Losing Their Best Players If Emery Continues As Arsenal&rsquo;s Manager.</p>\r\n<p>lacazette And Aubameyang Recently Liked A Picture On Instagram Stating That Unai Emery Should Be Sacked And It Seems The Arsenal Board Is Finally Realizing The Players Are Tired Of Unai Emery Which Suggests The Reason Behind Their Deliberation To Take A Decision After The Southampton Frustration.</p>\r\n<p>there Are Reports Unai Emery Will Be Sacked This Week And He Might Be Replaced With Mikel Arteta Or Freddie Ljungberg. Arteta Was Arsenal&rsquo;s First Choice To Take Over From Arsene Wenger But His Lack Of Professional Managerial Experience Was The Reason The Arsenal Hierarchy Doubted His Appointment. Ljungberg Is Really Rated By The Arsenal Board And They Feel He Can Do A Good Job To Help The Young Players Develop Their Full Potential.</p>\r\n<p>arsenal Is Known For A Philosophy And Tradition And That Is Why The Gunners Don&rsquo;t Want To Make Another Decision In Sacking Emery And Replacing Him With An Average Manager.</p>\r\n<p>mikel Arteta Has Spent A Few Years Working With Pep Guardiola And He Has Helped Players Like Raheem Sterling And Leroy Sane Develop Their Game To Be World Class Wingers And That Alone Is What Interests The Arsenal Hierarchy. Freddie Ljungberg On The Other Hand Did A Good Job With The Academy Before He Was Promoted As The Arsenal Assistant Manager As The Gunners Try To Integrate Youth Players Into Team Set Up.</p>\r\n<p>both Ex-players Are Familiar With The Club, The Tradition And Goals Of The Club Having Won Titles While Playing Under Arsene Wenger. Freddie Was Part Of Wenger&rsquo;s Golden Generation While Arteta Was Part Of The Team That Won Wenger 2 Fa Cups Back To Back To End Arsenal Trophy Droughts.</p>\r\n<p>a Lot Of Managers Are Also Being Considered Which Includes Max Allegri And Patrick Vieira But Arteta Or Freddie Are The Top Two Choices The Arsenal Hierarchy Has.</p>\r\n<p>unai Emery Is Most Likely To Leave This Week. A Bad Performance At The Europa League Means His Arsenal Managerial Career Is Over. We All Await The Decision By The Arsenal Board In Coming Days.</p>\r\n<p>dear Arsenal Supporters, Would You Love Mikel Arteta Or Freddie Ljungberg As Arsenal\\\'s Next Manager?</p>', '1574719735_thump.jpg', '2019-11-25 22:30:32', 1),
(18, 'Okpalaugo', 'Okpalaugo.chukwuka1@gmail.com', 'Epl: Referees Chief Admits Var Made Wrong Decisions For Arsenal, Man Utd', '<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">professional Game Match Officials Board (pgmol) Chief, Mike Riley, Has Admitted Video Officials Incorrectly Overturned Four Key Decisions That The On-field Referee Got Correct In The Premier League, Sportsmail Reports.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">one Of These Include Arsenal&rsquo;s Disallowed Winner Against Crystal Palace.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">sokratis Saw His Late Goal Awarded By Referee Martin Atkinson At The Emirates, Only For Var To Rule It Out And The Game Ended 2-2.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">at Meetings With Premier League Managers And Shareholders, Pgmol Felt That The Goal Should Have Stood, As One Of Four Occasions This Season When The Var Should Not Have Intervened.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">the Other Var Mistakes Included Everton Defender Michael Keane&rsquo;s Slight Step On Brighton Striker, Aaron Connolly, Which Was Let Go By The Referee But Was Overturned And A Spot-kick Rewarded On Review.<br />everton Went On To Lose The Game 3-2.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">two More Similar Incidents Occurred When Manchester United&rsquo;s Daniel James Went Down Under A Challenge From Norwich Defender Ben Godfrey, While Watford Forward Gerard Deulofeu Did The Same Under Minimal Contact By Chelsea Midfielder Jorginho.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">both Were Waved Away By The On-field Referee. Both Were Overturned By Var And Penalties.</p>', '1574720589_thump.jpeg', '2019-11-25 22:32:06', 1),
(19, 'Okpalaugo', 'Okpalaugo.chukwuka1@gmail.com', 'Messi Reveals Why He Won Ballon Dâ€™or Awards', '<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">barcelona Captain, Lionel Messi, Has Admitted He Won All Of His Ballon D&rsquo;or Prizes, Because Of How Successful The Club Was.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">messi, 32, Has Won The Award In 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 And 2015.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">only Cristiano Ronaldo Has Won The Award As Many Times.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">&ldquo;it Is A Beautiful Recognition And Perhaps The Most Special Was The First,&rdquo; Messi Told Otro.</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\">&ldquo;it Is Something That Comes From The Collective. Without Having Achieved All The Collective Successes That We Had To Achieve, I Wouldn&rsquo;t Have Been Able To Get These Individual Awards.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p Style=\\\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; Padding: 0px; Border: 0px; Font-size: 16px; Vertical-align: Baseline; Font-family: \\\'pt Serif\\\', Sans-serif; Line-height: 24.8px; Font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Widows: 1;\\\"><span Style=\\\"font-variant-numeric: Normal; Font-variant-east-asian: Normal; Line-height: 24.8px;\\\">messi Will Again Be Among The Favourites To Win The Ballon D&rsquo;or This Year, Having Enjoyed A Fine 2019 For Barcelona.</span></p>', '1574720885_thump.jpg', '2019-11-25 22:31:53', 1),
(20, 'Okpalaugo', 'Okpalaugo.chukwuka1@gmail.com', 'Anthony Joshua Lands In Saudi Arabia, Ready For Quiz', '<p>san Francisco, November 25, (thewill) &ndash; Anthony Joshua Landed Safely In Saudi Arabia Ahead Of His Rematch With Andy Ruiz Jr On December 7 And The Briton Is Promising To Produce A Performance To Remember When The Pair Enter The Ring.</p>\r\n<p>joshua, Who Was Handed His First Professional Defeat By Ruiz Jr Earlier This Year At Madison Square Garden In New York, Is Fighting In A Bid To Reclaim The Wba, Ibf, Wbo And Ibo Belts And Set Up A Unification Fight In 2020 With Wbc Champion Deontay Wilder.</p>\r\n<p>the 30-year-old Was All Smiles On Arrival With His Entourage As He Was Met By Some Fans And Attention Now Turns To Avenging Defeat With A Performance That Boxing Fans Will Speak Of For Years To Come.</p>\r\n<p>the Heavyweight Division Belts On The Line And Joshua&rsquo;s Credibility At Stake, There Is A Lot Of Pressure On The Watford-born Fighter Ahead Of The Rematch.</p>\r\n<p>but Joshua Appears Relaxed Despite The Pressure And Was In High Spirits As He Arrived At King Khalid Airport In Riyadh.</p>\r\n<p>&lsquo;it&rsquo;s Going To Be An Incredible Night And I&rsquo;m Thrilled So Many Of My Fans Are Going To Be There, Particularly From The Uk,&rsquo; Joshua Said.</p>\r\n<p>&lsquo;it&rsquo;ll Definitely Be A Night People Will Tell Their Grandchildren They Were At, One Of Those Iconic Evenings Of Boxing. Everyone From Saudi Has Been Brilliant To Work With.&rsquo;</p>\r\n<p>now Having Touched Down In The Country, Joshua Will Set-up His Pre-fight Training Camp In A Bid To Acclimatise In The Build-up To The Fight.</p>\r\n<p>the &lsquo;clash On The Dunes&rsquo;, As The Fight Is Being Dubbed, Is The First World Heavyweight Boxing Title Fight To Be Held In The Middle East.</p>\r\n<p>joshua And Defending Champion Ruiz Jr Will Fight At The Custom-built 15,000 Seat Diriyah Arena In The Heart Of A Unesco World Heritage Site.</p>\r\n<p>victory Is Essential For Joshua If He Is To Get His Career Back On Track With 2020 Set To Be Another Box-office Year In The Heavyweight Division</p>', '1574860752_thump.jpg', '2019-11-27 13:23:53', 1),
(23, 'Okpalaugo', 'Okpalaugo.chukwuka1@gmail.com', 'Nollywood Actor Zubby Michael Appointed Special Adviser To Anambra State Governor', '<p>zubby Micheal Has Been Appointed As A Special Advisor On Media To The Governor Of Anambra State, Willie Obiano.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>the Actor Announced The Good News Via His Instagram Page On Monday, November 25, 2019, Where He Shared A Photo Of Himself Holding What Appears To Be His Appointment Letter.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\\\"duty Calls #saonmedia #doings #nawedeyhere #blessup\\\" He Captioned The Photo.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>congratulations To Zubby Michael On His Latest Appointment. Zubby Michael Joins The List Of Nollywood Stars Who Have Taken On Political Appointments.</p>', '1574868084_thump.jpg', '2019-11-27 15:22:10', 1),
